# <@ .Name @>

A thin `llz` extension (`kind: tool`) scaffolded by `llz extension new`. It wraps
the external tool `<@ .Tool @>`: `recipe.yaml`'s `check:` argv invokes it directly.

There is no logic to unit-test here — `<@ .Tool @>` is the tested unit, upstream —
so `llz extension lint` requires no `*_test.go`. Just keep the manifest argv-only
(no inline `sh -c "…"`).

```sh
llz extension lint .
```
